---
title: Miso & Coconut Chicken Curry with Jasmine Rice & Crispy Shallots
description: With tender chicken, colourful veggies and an infusion of ginger and garlic, this coconut sauce is mild enough for picky eaters but has a deep flavour that will still keep the grown-ups satisfied.
